cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.HC. 

The paper discusses methods for improved video retrieval, which is a topic related to information retrieval (IR) and multimedia (MM). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.MM are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a system that uses dialog to retrieve videos, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and human-computer interaction (HCI), making cs.CL and cs.HC likely sub-categories as well. Finally, the proposed system also leverages the content of the videos, which involves computer vision (CV), making cs.CV a possible sub-category.
